{"tid":275393,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(集思廣益) 所謂既神駒屈葉狗跪長毛, 唯一既證人係蝗后?","createTime":"2017-06-08T04:03:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T14:48:40.000Z","uid":37264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fd3d3e05b0d5beecfae398b8f3d983a7794fd43f","tid":275393,"uid":37264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:03:09.000Z","msg":"有冇人覺得呢件事好古怪?"},{"pid":"51a458925a630848c7ca2adb766bb9424a6179cc","tid":275393,"uid":4389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:39:58.000Z","msg":"而家口同鼻拗，個看更佬並無因科學館衝擊去坐監，無留案底可以繼續做看更。長毛，甄燊港又唔會趟熱狗渾水出黎澄清，可能會變無頭公案。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/08/121637_09b32276c0c41e57e143d4e042510afd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F08%2F121637_09b32276c0c41e57e143d4e042510afd.jpg&h=60a3daf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n比黃洋達利用做白手套幾風騷，連樣都唔夠膽出，只係露個豬閪老婆樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b91012457b382a40e7777a1285acecc4e75fd394","tid":275393,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:40:27.000Z","msg":"咁神駒都係聽人講<br />\n神駒屈人都唔係第一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3e58248d61a8d1168e4a9c3263bb0979ee89906","tid":275393,"uid":22701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:43:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁神駒都係聽人講<br />\n神駒屈人都唔係第一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n熱狗屈人又何嘗需要證據"},{"pid":"55e7db61b4c1e889e28efced14abd1829c7d7ad3","tid":275393,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:59:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁神駒都係聽人講<br />\n神駒屈人都唔係第一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n熱狗屈人又何嘗需要證據</blockquote><br />\n但神駒都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"